The '''Overden''' was the ruling body of the planet [[Selonia/Legends|Selonia]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. A radical [[Selonian/Legends|Selonian]] political group, it allied itself with the [[Sacorrian Triad]] during the [[Corellian Crisis|First Corellian Insurrection]].

